Me:
&quot;Hmmmm maybe ill play a ranked today even though i hate it, just to improve my chances when the new season starts&quot;

The Universe:
&quot;good idea, ill play as well but on the enemy team.&quot;

Me:
&quot;No, please, no, i just want a good fair game.&quot;

The Universe:
&quot;LIFE AIN&#039;T FAIR BITCH!&quot;

Me:
&quot;Please, what do i have to do?&quot;

The Universe:
&quot;I want you to look in the dictionary.&quot;

Me:
&quot;Okay, what word am i looking for?&quot;

The Universe:
&quot;The word &#039;Rape&#039;&quot;

Me:
&quot;Sure?... But theres no definition, just a picture.&quot;

The Universe:
&quot;What the picture of?&quot;

Me: 
&quot;Its just a picture of a league team?&quot;

The Universe:
&quot;look at your screen %%%%.&quot;

Me:
&quot;NOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!!!!!&quot;

The Universe:
&quot;Have fun :D&quot;
